{"product_id": "10150", "page": 1, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "14 January", "text": "This game is fun as hell! I`ve been playing for 20hrs only, but I can tell this game is worth the price.\nI play it on a laptop that isn`t even meant for gaming; but it can play 720p, 60fps, on all high graphic settings very well.\nYou can also use a ps4 controller (which I prefer) and it plays well too. The game starts off with a linear mission intro. But after a couple missions, used to get you acclimated to the game mechanics, the game`s semi-open world mechanics come to light. It is fun actually traversing through the city like a Spiderman-Hulk hybrid, in order to get to the next mission.\n8/10 would recommend. Voice acting, character models, colour palette of the city, and lack of other activities to do in free roam are the only downsides for me so far.", "hours": 20.5, "user_id": "76561198373971871", "username": "mckennyndifor", "products": 6, "early_access": false}
