{"product_id": "344340", "page": 2, "page_order": 2, "recommended": true, "date": "2020-01-22", "text": "Haven't played FOF8 yet, but FOF7 in itself is the best football simulator around.  Can go nearly as deep as you want it to be, all the way down to coaching the actual game.  All of the systems feel realistic and you can't only look at a players rating number.  Their weight and height matter (like a tall WR or QB will do better than shorter ones for example).\nI've been playing this series since FoF2004, and each one seems to somehow be a better sim. HaHa.\nIf you like American Football, and you like stat simulators, this is the best American Football sim around.\nI hope to grab FoF8 on sale sometime, but until then I am PERFECTLY happy with FOF7 as a single player experience.", "hours": 522.3, "user_id": "76561198034102404", "username": "reiperxhc", "products": 360, "early_access": false}
