{"product_id": "230820", "page": 2, "page_order": 5, "recommended": true, "date": "2021-12-08", "text": "I would totally recommend this game to anyone who wants to play a game without struggling to find the solutions to the challenges.\n1) It has a cute storyline and a beautiful message about\n.\n2) 8 short Audio Stories that you can hear anytime you want - extras.\n3) Beautiful Music AND Artstyle.\n4) Short Length (5-6 hours if you want to run it or 10-15 hours if you want to take your time and enjoy the sceneries, characters etc).\n5) AWESOME \"LITTLE PETS IN CUSTOM\" STICKERS\n.", "hours": 28.8, "user_id": "76561198959978196", "username": "‚ò†Ô∏è Dark Lady ‚ò†", "products": 48, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "230820", "page": 2, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2021-11-28", "text": "Honestly these guys are like  old school LucasArt. Every point and click game they put out is just amazing.\nDeponia had humor,\nwas grim and serious and this one is lightweight, bright and innocent.\nBeautiful hand painted maps, sweet voice acting, characters so full of life, so diverse and unique that will make you explore  everything and talk to everyone. On some puzzles you might be lost a bit so guide would be recommended or use a magic wand in game which gives you tips, but otherwise they aren't that demanding if you have any past experience in playing Point and click games.\nPros:\n‚úÖ Voice acting is wonderful\n‚úÖ A lot of maps to explore\n‚úÖ Very diverse characters\n‚úÖ  Beautiful hand painted visuals\nCons:\n‚ùå Some puzzles are a tiny bit more difficult but otherwise nothing else really\nPersonal score: ‚òÖ‚òÖ‚òÖ‚òÖ‚òÖüèÜ\nü§ñFinal words: Mousewood is full of life and beuatiful. Go explore it, I bet you'll enjoy the adventure.Magic and wizards await because :", "hours": 12.1, "username": "Tyrannical Ambition", "products": 612, "early_access": false}
