{"product_id": "342450", "page": 1, "page_order": 6, "recommended": false, "date": "15 September, 2020", "text": "Sadly can't really recommend this game. I went in really hoping I'd love it but there are very few choices to make, no ability to create or direct your character and it can be a long way between 'decisive checkpoint' and 'end game'. Overall I really hoped it would be like a Choice of Games game with images but it had none of the depth of a CoG game. I'd definitely recommend you'd spend your money on those and use your imagination than settle for Sword Daughter. It could have been an excellent game if you'd had the option to choose your characters personality a bit more with more choices in game that would do this. Even if they don't have a direct effect on the ending.", "hours": 1.4, "username": "Emi", "products": 224, "early_access": false}
