{"product_id": "344340", "page": 4, "page_order": 3, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-07-21", "text": "I am a big time fan of football and have always searched for a game that allowed me to take the place of an NFL General Manager and call all the shots. With Front Office Football Seven, I can do what I've always wanted to do. This game gives an in-depth experience of running a football franchise and I couldn't be more pleased with what is offered. I could play this game for years and never get bored. If you are a fan of football and find yourself constantly analyzing rosters, players, draft prospects, etc; please do yourself a huge favor and buy this game. You will not get bored.", "hours": 186.0, "user_id": "76561198315920005", "username": "Milianaire", "products": 243, "early_access": false}
