{"product_id": "344340", "page": 4, "page_order": 7, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-05-30", "text": "A love of text sims,this is the best one I've played yet. If you are a fan of american football this is a need in your library. Its pure realism simple as that. After a good bit of time into this game and many seasons I can say i fully recommend this. Whether you want just to sign player and let the ai handle the depth charts for you,Or take every little control over the game from ticket sales,to stadium renovations,to strategy its all in your control. My recommendations for the next version are these (This game has very few faults).\n-College and NFL in 1 D1 colleges,work your way through the gm ladder\n-If no college gm mode,then have college players stats year by year,and awards etc\n-Simplyifyed depth chart option (advanced would be now simplyfied would be something like madden)\n-simplified formation option (same thing as above)\n-Draft class maker,Roster file maker,coach file maker (A simple easy to use tool shipped with the game to make these)\n-Customization! People love there custom leagues and I think this is a need perhaps OOTP style customization?\n-I appreciate and like the simple presentation of the game but it could use some updating\n-Other teams moving cities (is this already in?)", "hours": 196.7, "username": "PopePasta", "products": 1272, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
