{"product_id": "31920", "page": 5, "page_order": 6, "recommended": false, "date": "2020-07-16", "text": "Okay, hear me out. This game is pretty fun, but let me tell you what. When it comes time to play Scopa, you're going to want to throw yourself into a ravine. You're going to want to peel your skin off and feed it to a fish. You're going to wish you were in a refrigerator for the rest of your life with no human contact. No matter how good you are at this game, or how much you *get* it, you won't be winning. It's mandatory for your progress through the rest of the game, so just... don't. Just play another Nancy Drew and enjoy a Scopa-free life while you still have the chance.", "hours": 3.0, "username": "bamfxfrenchie", "products": 54, "found_funny": 6, "early_access": false}
