{"product_id": "314020", "page": 7, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2020-06-16", "text": "Pro: Atmosphere, easy to 100%, relatively pleasant to play.\nCon: Almost no settings/options, no difficulty, subpar controls\nAside atmosphere, game is very minimalist, controls are clunky and it will take you around 90 minutes to clear it 100% with no replay value.\nI liked it but is it worth 4 dollars in 2020 ? I don't know. At one point some work was put into it and it should be rewarded but ... hard to put a price tag on this one.\nRecommended if you look for an easy, fast game to 100%. You will have a pleasant time but this is not the kind of game you should spend your money on if your budget is a bit tight, even if you like the genre, this game is far from being the best at what it does.", "hours": 1.8, "username": "Dantounet", "products": 611, "early_access": false}
