{"product_id": "342450", "page": 4, "page_order": 3, "recommended": false, "date": "2017-07-24", "text": "Trite, stereo-typical and cliche-ridden are the nicest things I can say about the text of this CYOA tale. I am not sure there is a massive audience for a story where you play a pathetic damsel in distress that every man instantly falls in love with. Luckily, your heart belongs to the handsome half-elf, Gavin, in 21 of the games 22 endings. And dont worry, the Sword Daughter of titular fame never actually does anything. Cant have the lead character showing any agency when ... Gavin... can save you.\nNot worth your money, or the two hours it would take to complete all endings and 100%", "hours": 1.9, "username": "Cyquinias", "products": 698, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
